Before use:

A)install socat on your Pfsense 2.0.1:

setenv PACKAGESITE ftp://ftp-archive.freebsd.org/pub/FreeBSD-Archive/ports/i386/packages-8.1-release/Latest/
or
setenv PACKAGESITE ftp://ftp-archive.freebsd.org/pub/FreeBSD-Archive/ports/amd64/packages-8.1-release/Latest/

pkg_add -r socat.tbz

rehash


B)add "stats socket /tmp/haproxy.socket level admin" in your Haproxy "Global Advanced pass thru" settings


C)install .inc and .php files in respectively /usr/local/www/widgets/includes and /usr/local/www/widgets/widgets


D)add widget via pfsense dashboard
